#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.51"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.51:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.51:0.2"
msgid "5. Sāmaññavagga"
msgstr "5. Similarity"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.51:0.3"
msgid "51. Diṭṭhadhammanibbānasutta"
msgstr "51. Extinguishment in the Present Life"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.51:1.1"
msgid "“‘Diṭṭhadhammanibbānaṃ diṭṭhadhammanibbānan’ti, āvuso, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend, they speak of ‘extinguishment in the present life’."

msgctxt "an9.51:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, diṭṭhadhammanibbānaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"In what way did the Buddha speak of extinguishment in the present life?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.51:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāvuso, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja "
"viharati."
msgstr ""
"“First, take a mendicant who, quite secluded from sensual pleasures … enters "
"and remains in the first absorption."

msgctxt "an9.51:2.2"
msgid ""
"Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, diṭṭhadhammanibbānaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā pariyāyena … pe "
"…."
msgstr ""
"To this extent the Buddha spoke of extinguishment in the present life in a "
"qualified sense. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an9.51:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma "
"saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, paññāya cassa disvā āsavā "
"parikkhīṇā honti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of "
"neither perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation "
"of perception and feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, their defilements "
"come to an end."

msgctxt "an9.51:3.2"
msgid ""
"Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, diṭṭhadhammanibbānaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā "
"nippariyāyenā”ti."
msgstr ""
"To this extent the Buddha spoke of extinguishment in the present life in an "
"unqualified sense.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.51:3.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.51:3.4"
msgid "Sāmaññavaggo pañcamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.455"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an9.51:4.1"
msgid "Sambādho kāyasakkhī paññā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.51:4.2"
msgid "Ubhatobhāgo sandiṭṭhikā dve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.51:4.3"
msgid "Nibbānaṃ parinibbānaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an9.51:4.4"
msgid "Tadaṅgadiṭṭhadhammikena cāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "an9.51:4.5"
msgid "Paṭhamo paṇṇāsako samatto."
msgstr ""
